                        meaningful service work.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Projects</h3>
                    <p>
                        Find service projects where you can contribute
                        your time and skills.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Categories</h3>
                    <p>
                        Browse projects by areas such as environment,
                        education, community service, and wellness.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

    </main>

    <%- include("partials/footer") %>
